title: Poppy Playtime 005 #Shorts
author: Jake Fellman
description:
Watch all of my horror animations here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LvvPIc2DnG8&list=PLHTiqada2E2BlhjkZkYoONCth1hhyy8rh&index=2

Behind the scenes: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FRI4ixSn2sA&list=PLe5Frw1C-LJA10ZMARlsTyGBkIHiBZ7xf&index=25

Poppy Playtime is a unique, horror-puzzle adventure.  In this game, you play as an ex-employee of a corporate giant in the toy manufacturing industry, exploring an abandoned factory in the aftermath of an unethical scientific experiment gone wrong. 

Music: "Sleepwalk" by Santo & Johnny
